short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Experience the mesmerizing power of *Herrscher Elysia* from *Honkai Impact* with this stunning live wallpaper

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This live wallpaper brings Herrscher Elysia to life, showcasing her stunning abilities and ethereal beauty. Surrounded by glowing energy and intricate visual effects, she commands attention with every movement.
